═══════════════════════════════════════

Solara is a rolling Arch-based distro.
Elegant by default, not by accident.

To install: Run 'solara-install' or follow the guide at:
https://github.com/ravecorelabs/solara/wiki

Quick start:
  • Wi-Fi: nmtui or nmcli
  • Install: sudo solara-install
  • Desktop: SDDM auto-login as 'solara'

